\b\fs32 Pain management, prescription opioid mortality, and the CDC: is the devil in the data? \b0\fs24\par
\par
\fs20 Michael E Schatman\dn8 1,2\up0  \fs24\par
\fs20 Stephen J Ziegler\dn8 3\up0  \fs24\par
\par
